				<wikidot:authorName>Ellie3</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3656445</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is my entry for <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-11220181/very-unofficial-and-not-sponsored-djkaktus-contest-thread#post-4221846">DjKaktus's Unofficial Contest</a>.</p> <p>This tale is dedicated to my great-grandmother, who passed away about three months ago.</p> <p>It was very challenging to write this, and I cried through most of it. But I hope you all enjoy it.</p> <p>(And it has a word count of 499, which is neat. That also means it's below the word limit of 500.)</p> <p>Big thanks to the following people:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575520244" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span> for being a beta reader in the SCPD Discord and helping me figure out a title.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magnadeus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3499685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575520244" alt="magnadeus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3499685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magnadeus" >magnadeus</a></span> for being a beta reader in the SCPD Discord.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psychicprogrammer" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5299606&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575520244" alt="psychicprogrammer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5299606)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psychicprogrammer" >psychicprogrammer</a></span> for being a beta reader in the SCPD Discord too, as well as helping me figure out a title too.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/odstdragon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3228312&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575520244" alt="ODSTDRAGON" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3228312)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/odstdragon" >ODSTDRAGON</a></span> for being a beta reader in the Cimmerian's Discord.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-north" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4695462&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575520244" alt="Doctor North" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4695462)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-north" >Doctor North</a></span> for also being a beta reader in the Cimmerian's Discord.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/knightalaska" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4791424&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575520244" alt="KnightAlaska" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4791424)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/knightalaska" >KnightAlaska</a></span> for being a beta reader in the SCPD Discord.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575520244" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span> for their crit in the SCPD Discord.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&a